Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerry’s Ice Cream Triple Caramel Chunk 458 ML

Caramel lovers won’t want to miss a single moment of this must-eat caramel trilogy, starring creamy caramel ice cream, gooey caramel swirls, and chewy caramel chunks. They probably won’t want it to end, either. Now that's caramel-icious flavour filled deliciousness.

It is decadently delicious proof that when it comes to caramel, good things do indeed come in threes. Dig in! Again. And Again. If you’re like us, sometimes you crave nothing more than caramel, and lots of it. Yet the buttery sweet treat comes in so many forms, and when the cravings kick in, it can be hard to choose. There’s caramel icecream, caramel sauce, and fudge-covered caramel cups. Lucky for you, Ben & Jerry’s Triple Caramel Chunk combines every option into one rich, creamy, and super-indulgent caramel filled icecream concoction. There is even the perfect amount of fudge chunks thrown in to push this must-eat caramel dessert right over the top. So grab a spoon, settle in, and dig in to an ice cream tub of this caramel thrillogy of decadent delights!

You can also feel good about satisfying your ice cream cravings knowing that Triple Caramel Chunk, like all of Ben & Jerry’s frozen dessert flavours, uses only non-GMO-sourced ingredients and eggs from cage-free hens. Fairtrade certified producers supply the cocoa, sugar, and vanilla; and all of our super premium ice cream pint and frozen dessert packaging is responsibly sourced.

Ben & Jerry's Triple Caramel Chunk ice cream pint

Caramel Ice Cream with a Caramel Swirl and a Chocolatey Covered Caramel Chunk

All of Ben & Jerry’s ice cream is made with non-GMO sourced ingredients & cage-free eggs

Includes Fairtrade certified cocoa, sugar, and vanilla

Kosher certified dairy; Halal Certified

Ben & Jerry’s uses responsibly sourced packaging

Products.FullDescription: Ben & Jerry's Half Baked Ice Cream
Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerry’s Ice Cream Half Baked 458 ML

A delectable dance of Chocoate Chip Cookie Dough and Chocolate Fudge Brownie. Vanilla ice cream and chocolate icecream with cookie dough and fudge brownies—it’s hard to imagine a better icecream combination. Ben and Jerrys Half Baked ice cream, which got its name because the cookie dough isn’t baked, but the brownies are—has been a bestselling flavour since we first decided to combine our classic homemade ice cream creations back in 2000.

Cookie Dough, with big chunks of chocolate chip cookie dough surrounded by vanilla ice cream, was created back in 1984 at our very first Scoop Shop after we received an anonymous flavour suggestion. It continues as a flavour phenomenon to this very day. Chocolate Fudge Brownie is a fan-favourite chocolate extravaganza, mixing chocolate ice cream with ridiculously delicious Greyston Bakery brownies. It’s been satisfying chocolate lovers since 1991. We know it can be hard to choose between those two legendary flavours. With our Half Baked ice cream tub, you don’t have to! We work with Fairtrade-certified producers for all the cocoa, sugar, and vanilla in our recipes. Our Caring Dairy farmers produce all the kosher-certified milk and cream in a sustainable way. Greyston Bakery, one of the largest social enterprises in the USA, provides the sumptuous brownies for this and all of our frozen dessert flavours.

All our ice cream is made with non-GMO-sourced ingredients and cage-free eggs. This ice-cream pint, like every pint we make, features responsibly sourced packaging.

Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerry’s Ice Cream The Tonight Dough® 458 ML

Caramel and chocolate ice creams with crunchy chocolate cookie swirls and gobs of chocolate chip cookie dough and peanut butter cookie dough. This frozen ice cream tub is simply over the top, but there’s more to this story than just chunks and swirls.

One of our most popular flavors since launching in 2015, The Tonight Dough was created with Jimmy Fallon to celebrate his takeover of The Tonight Show – the longest running talk show in TV history. As big, bold, and amazing as Fallon himself, the flavour stands out as one of Ben & Jerry’s chunkiest, doughiest, most-over-the-top ice creams yet. But the flavour’s success is even sweeter because Fallon donates all proceeds from the sale of The Tonight Dough to the SeriousFun Children’s Network.

Feel good about your choice of dessert knowing you are helping children with serious illnesses and their families enjoy life-changing experiences at a camp that fosters growth and happiness – free of charge. The best ice cream is nothing without great ingredients. Like all Ben & Jerry’s flavors, The Tonight Dough is made with non-GMO-sourced ingredients and eggs from cage-free hens. Fairtrade certified producers supply the cocoa, sugar, and vanilla, and our product chills inside your freezer in responsibly sourced packaging.

Products.SmallFormatDescription: Streets Vegan Cornetto
Products.FullDescription: Streets Vegan Cornetto
Products.RichDescription:
CORNETTO ICE CONFECTION VEGAN VANILLA 360 ML

The Cornetto Made with Soy consists of a delicious, crispy baked wafer, coated inside from top to bottom with a chocolatey layer, combined with a delicious vanilla soy ice cream and dark chocolatey pieces. It is suitable for Vegans. For over 50 years we’ve been perfecting our Cornetto recipe to make the taste of every Cornetto ice cream even better than the last, taking your taste buds on a delicious journey, from the tantalising topping, through the smooth ice cream down to the crispy wafer cone and of course the chocolatey tip. We have now perfected our recipe to allow us to use soy based ice cream that keeps the creamy texture that Cornetto is famous for. Spica, an ice cream manufacturer from Naples, was passionate about ice cream, loving creamy texture, delicious flavours and quality ingredients. One day, Spica found a way to spread ice cream passion to everyone, creating a formula that could not fail. The great idea was to cover the inside of the cone with a chocolatey layer, allowing the wafer to keep its crispiness when filled with ice cream, this breakthrough innovation “Cornetto” was born from that moment on, people could enjoy their crispy, delicious Cornetto whenever they want. Now, we have expanded our range so that Cornetto truly is for everyone. Creamy and Crunchy, the perfect match. Try a Cornetto today! Find us on Facebook, Instagram and Twitter and let us know about your Cornetto experience!

A crispy baked wafer coated from top to bottom with a chocolatey layer, combined with vanilla flavoured soy ice cream, chocolatey pieces and hazelnuts

Available in a 4 multipack

Vanilla flavour soy ice cream in a wafer cone (12%), with a chocolate flavour coating (12%) and dark chocolate pieces (2%)

Creamy and Crunchy, the perfect match

Suitable for Vegans

Products.RichDescription:
Ben & Jerry’s Non-Dairy Frozen Dessert Chocolate Fudge Brownie 458 ML

Our Non Dairy Chocolate Fudge Brownie ice cream tub is a decadent chocolate experience with fabulously fudgy brownies. It's a 100% vegan certified Non-Dairy version of one of our classic Ben & Jerry’s hit icecream flavours.

Some might call it impossible, we just call it non dairy dessert magic! It took three years of tasting and tweaking to perfect Ben & Jerry’s Non-Dairy recipe. Ultimately, almond milk is what made the magic happen, creating the smooth and creamy texture you crave. Of course, achieving all the funky chunks and sweet swirls – without dairy, eggs, or honey – was no simple task. Yet the work (and wait) was worth it. In fact, the finished product is so good that, in the case of Chocolate Fudge Brownie, many devout dairy fans are giving praise to the almond milk alternative.

Equally awesome is that the brownies in this Non-Dairy fan favourite come from Greyston Bakery, located in Yonkers, New York. Since 1982, this social enterprise has been battling poverty by offering education and employment to residents who need it most.The good vibes don’t stop there. All of Ben & Jerry’s dairy-free desserts are made with non-GMO-sourced certified vegan ingredients and Fairtrade certified sugar, cocoa, and vanilla. Not to mention that the dessert goes from our Vermont factory to your freezer in responsibly sourced packaging.

Includes Fairtrade certified sugar, cocoa, & vanilla

Ben & Jerry's Non-Dairy flavour creations are made with almond milk.

Kosher certified, Vegan

Ben & Jerry’s uses responsibly sourced packaging.

Products.RichDescription:
BEN & JERRY`S ICE CREAM CHUNKY MONKEY 458 ML 10000215
Banana ice cream with fudge chunks and walnuts: the nuttiest chocolatey-chunkiest concoction-gone-bananas icecream you'll ever go ape for.

This taste sensation was suggested by a college student in New Hampshire, way back in 1988. The idea seemed so perfect that we got started on it right away. Of course, we had to monkey around with bunches of test batches to get the flavour just right, but we did, and the rest is history. Twenty-two years on we made it even sweeter with the addition of Fairtrade bananas. Today this ice cream tub remains one of Ben & Jerry’s most iconic flavours.

Every time you plunge your spoon into a frozen tub Chunky Monkey icecream you’re guaranteed to scoop up huge chocolate chunks and perfectly crunchy walnuts all surrounded by impossibly smooth banana ice cream. It’s a monkey’s dream. Well, actually, plenty of ice cream lovers seem to think it’s pretty dreamy too. Note: No monkeys were harmed in the making of this dessert (well, okay, maybe some bananas got a little roughed up). Enjoy!

Ben & Jerry’s gets all our cocoa, sugar, vanilla and bananas from Fairtrade certified producers. Our ice cream is made with non-GMO sourced ingredients and cage-free eggs. We always use responsibly sourced packaging.

Our products are the same delicious products that are proudly processed at our factory in Kelso NSW. You will start to see these changes on our packaging from mid-November 2020 through to March 2021. Products will be available featuring both a “Made in” and “Packed in” claim during this period.

Products.FullDescription: Connoisseur Mango & Coconut Ice Cream
Products.RichDescription: Taste the extremes of Australia Queensland, bathed in sunshine, is the perfect place to grow sweet, juicy mangoes. We take the fragrant mango syrup and swirl it through smooth coconut flavoured ice cream. This exotic flavour is then locked away inside of a layer of premium white chocolate and toasted coconut. A tantalisingly tropical flavour.

AdditionalAttributes.description: Taste the extremes of Australia Queensland, bathed in sunshine, is the perfect place to grow sweet, juicy mangoes. We take the fragrant mango syrup and swirl it through smooth coconut flavoured ice cream. This exotic flavour is then locked away inside of a layer of premium white chocolate and toasted coconut. A tantalisingly tropical flavour.
